title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
